What you need to know:  Safaricom CEO Peter Ndegwa announced that Safaricom will sponsor four young drivers — McRae Kimathi, Jeremy Wahome, Hamza Anwar and Maxine Wahome — in a Sh25 million package, the biggest in rallying since the BAT days for individual drivers in the 1990sShe said Kenya is thinking of hosting the Formula One one day and also developing e-sports